1. Kupio sam *polovinu* hleba. (I bought half a loaf of bread.)
2. Želim *polovinu* torte. (I want half of the cake.)
3. *Polovina* godine je prošla. (Half of the year has passed.)
4. Koliko *polovina* čokolade košta? (How much does half of the chocolate cost?)
5. Uzmite *polovinu* od te paprike. (Take half of that pepper.)
6. Preostala *polovina* pice je za vas. (The remaining half of the pizza is for you.)
7. *Polovina* učenika je bila odsutna. (Half of the students were absent.)
8. Idemo u šetnju *polovinom* dana. (We're going for a walk in the middle of the day.)
9. Koliko *polovina* ima 50? (How many halves are there in 50?)
10. Poklonio sam joj *polovinu* svog srca. (I gave her half of my heart.)